 currently in print-is an essential resource for students and lovers of dance.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aDancevReviews. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Dance / General.2bisacsh1 aCornfield, Robert, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030007617240uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030014652340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300146523423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300146523/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY